OL,3,CProgramme listings for MON 1 JUN
OL,4,G1405FCome Dine with Me
OL,5,     GPeterborough. Driving instructor
OL,6,     GChristine's guests are dreading
OL,7,     Gher meat-free menu, while
OL,8,     GChristine is anxious about
OL,9,     GRosie's feedback after she
OL,10,     Gcompared Moony's food to vomit.
OL,11,G1435FCome Dine with Me
OL,12,     GPeterborough. Mobile hairdresser
OL,13,     GBen plans a gourmet night, as he
OL,14,     Gentertains his guests with his
OL,15,     Gamazing body art, cooking skills
OL,16,     Gand pet crabs.
OL,17,G1510FCome Dine with Me
OL,18,     GPeterborough. Fridge salesman
OL,19,     GGregory serves up a Spanish menu
OL,20,     Gand a charm offensive.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
